data.description: Charming, well maintained and nicely updated home in the heart of Gatesville. This 3/2 with over 1200 sq ft of living has updated flooring and paint and a back yard you will absolutely love! Living area opens to the oversized kitchen/dining featuring stainless appliances. Good sized master suite has a large tile shower in bath. Guest rooms share hall bath with tile surround bath. Backyard is a shade tree oasis, will be the place to be on weekends and evenings underneath the impressive oaks. Great location just a few blocks to Main Street and easy access to Highway 36, this home is awaiting new owners today!
